dynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/52955/', '', 'Amantadine, Bremelanotide, Black cohosh, Ibuprofen, Naproxen', 'Codeine, Oliceridine, Naltrexone, Oxymorphone, Naloxone, Tapentadol, Butorphanol, Meperidine, Dezocine, Opium, Methadone, More', 1767369485);
